Package Report

Class ReportEntry

java.lang.Object
Report.ReportEntry
public class ReportEntry extends Object
Represents a single entry in a BTO booking report. Each entry contains information about an applicant and the project they successfully booked.

      public ReportEntry(String applicantName, String nric, int age, MaritalStatus maritalStatus, String projectName, String flatType, LocalDate bookingDate)
      Constructs a ReportEntry with the specified applicant and project details.
      Parameters:
      applicantName - the name of the applicant
      nric - the NRIC of the applicant
      age - the age of the applicant
      maritalStatus - the marital status of the applicant
      projectName - the name of the booked project
      flatType - the flat type booked (e.g., "2-Room", "3-Room")
      bookingDate - the date on which the flat was booked
